Ultra_-_Seven_Days,_Deluxe_Edition_(2011)_(digital)_(Minutemen-PhD)


Collects ULTRA: SEVEN DAYS #1-8 plus Bonus Materials! In Spring City, where superheroes blur the line between law enforcement and celebrity, Pearl Penalosa, AKA Ultra, is a workaholic. At the prestigious agency, Heroine Inc., she has earned a legion of fans, a nomination for 'Best Heroin of the Year,' and a perfect life. Well...almost perfect. A chance encounter with a mysterious fortune teller prophesizes true love for Pearl within seven days.
